 Fidelity Bank PLC, has rewarded over 1,140 customers with cash prizes in its Get Alert in Millions Season 5 (GAIM 5) promo. Speaking at the fifth monthly draw of the reward scheme held at the bank’s head office in Victoria Island, Lagos on Tuesday, Dr Ken Opara, Promo Chairman and Executive Director, Lagos and South-West Business of the bank who was represented by Lanre Showunmi the bank’s Chief Digital Officer, said, “Five months ago, we launched the GAIM 5 promo to reward our esteemed customers in demonstration of our commitment to improve their well-being and to help them imbibe a healthy savings habit. At the beginning of the promo, we earmarked a total of N125 million as cash prizes in weekly, monthly, and grand draws which would hold till the end of the campaign in July this year. “As of today, we have rewarded 1,140 customers with various sums of money comprising 1,100 customers that have won N10,000 each in 22 weekly consolation draws and 40 customers who have won N1 million each in the four monthly draws we have conducted this season.” The winners would receive their rewards at prize presentation events in their respective branches across the country next week.